platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Revenge is a dish served with epic property damage and plenty of attitude when a princess and her pet dragon decide theyre tired of getting captured. Its pure destructive joy guiding this royal duo over (and under) a gorgeous fantasy landscape of fleeing knights, treacherous traps, and mighty bosses to smash. The game pops with personalityand its simple controls, slick level design, and upgradable equipment keep the challenge fun and fresh.
